# /learn

Orchestrates reflection and contribution of learnings.

## Usage

```
/learn                       # Learn from current task
/learn {task-id}             # Learn from specific task
```

## What It Does

Executes in sequence:
1. `/reflect` - Compare plan vs outcome
2. `/contribute` - Add learnings to rules

